@startuml
title COLORS Web Application - Use Case Diagram
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor "User" as User

rectangle "COLORS Web Application" {
  usecase "Log In" as UC_Login
  usecase "Search Colors" as UC_Search
  usecase "Add Color" as UC_Add
  usecase "Log Out" as UC_Logout
}

User --> UC_Login
User --> UC_Search
User --> UC_Add
User --> UC_Logout

note right of UC_Search
Requires authenticated user session
and uses SearchColors API.
end note

note right of UC_Add
Requires authenticated user session
and uses AddColor API.
end note

/' UML diagram source for the COLORS assignment '/
@enduml
